<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is a synthesis of these two approaches:<=
/p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Sell stock to institutional investors=
