ned to comment=E2=80=9D <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/=
click/30484592.259448/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzL=
zIwMjMtMDItMDcvaHVkc29uLWJheS1jYXBpdGFsLXNhaWQtdG8tYW5jaG9yLWJlZC1iYXRoLWJl=
