<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">When David Solomon was a senior executive at G=
oldman Sachs Group Inc. and also a DJ, he and some of his advisers worried =
that he could not balance those two activities. =E2=80=9CSome advisers told=
 him to hang it up,=E2=80=9D a 2019 <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/30484592.259448/aHR0cHM6Ly9mb3J0dW5lLmNvbS9sb25nZm9ybS9nb=
2xkbWFuLXNhY2hzLWNlby1kYXZpZC1zb2xvbW9uLw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBff41d735=
" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D=
"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px=
; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-colo=
r: #ccc;"> Fortune profile</a> (<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/30484592.259448/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL=
2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjAtMDEtMzEvZG9uLXQtYmxpdHpzY2FsZS1hZ2FpbnN0LXlvdXJzZWxmP2Nt=
