ound-color: #ccc;"> once imagined</a> the Disney movie of Solomon=E2=80=99s=
 life:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I want to see the crusty older ban=
kers telling Solomon to give up his dreams of being a DJing investment bank=
er. =E2=80=9CDavid, you=E2=80=99re a good banker, one of the best. But this=
 DJing stuff won=E2=80=99t fly, not at Goldman Sachs, which as you know is =
one of Wall Street=E2=80=99s most storied institutions. You=E2=80=99ve got =
to give up these childish dreams, hang up your chunky headphones, and focus=
 on the work.=E2=80=9D And then Solomon will say =E2=80=9Cyes you=E2=80=99r=
e right, it=E2=80=99s for the best,=E2=80=9D and there will be a sad scene =
of him putting the headphones in a closet and giving them a long sad linger=
ing look, and then he will meet a wise old guru (Lloyd Blankfein) who will =
sing a little song telling him =E2=80=9Clook into your heart, it will tell =
you what to do, about the DJing.=E2=80=9D And then Solomon will sing the bi=
g showstopper song (=E2=80=9CHow Little I Care=E2=80=9D), the gist of which=
 is =E2=80=9Cactually I have decided that I can be both a successful invest=
ment banker and a DJ, watch out world.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But=C2=A0what if the crusty older bankers were=
 right? What if they pulled Solomon aside and were like =E2=80=9Cif you con=
tinue trying to be both CEO of Goldman Sachs and also a DJ, you will bring =
disgrace to yourself and the firm; it is simply too dangerous to combine th=
ose two activities,=E2=80=9D and Solomon ignored their advice and was like =
=E2=80=9Cno, you don=E2=80=99t understand, I am a uniquely talented investm=
ent-banker-and-DJ, I know that no one else has pulled it off before but I a=
m different, I will succeed,=E2=80=9D and they shook their heads sadly and =
walked away to mourn the destruction that they now knew was inevitable? And=
 then Solomon=E2=80=99s efforts to combine DJing and Goldman Sachs CEOing r=
eally did bring down the firm?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Frankly I cannot imagine how that would actual=
ly work =E2=80=94=C2=A0it=E2=80=99s just DJing, it=E2=80=99s fine, who care=
s =E2=80=94=C2=A0but this New York Times investigation with the remarkable =
headline =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/=
30484592.259448/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAyMy8wMi8wNS9idXNpbmVzcy9=
kYXZpZC1zb2xvbW9uLWRqLWdvbGRtYW4tc2FjaHMuaHRtbA/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB07=
b1e84f" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" st=
yle=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-widt=
h: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgroun=
d-color: #ccc;">The Blurred Lines Between Goldman C.E.O.=E2=80=99s Day Job =
and His D.J. Gig</a>=E2=80=9D brings us a tiny step closer to that outcome:=
</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Mr. Solomon=E2=80=99s hobby occasionally brush=
es up against his day job in ways that could pose potential conflicts of in=
terest, according to interviews with securities law experts and four people=
 who have worked with Mr. Solomon who were not authorized to speak publicly=
. Company executives and public officials typically try to minimize even mi=
nor conflicts because even the slightest hint of one can bring unwanted scr=
utiny and bad publicity.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Mr. Solomon has told senior Goldman executives=
 that he donates any profits he makes as a D.J. to charity. But Goldman emp=
loyees have sometimes helped him manage his D.J. schedule and his donations=
, three people who have worked with him said.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Through Goldman=E2=80=99s work in the music bu=
siness, he has also made at least one industry connection that helped him p=
ursue his hobby, raising questions about whether his opportunities have com=
e about because of his talent or his position as the leader of Wall Street=
=E2=80=99s most elite investment bank.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">For instance, Solomon apparently got to remix =
Whitney Houston=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9CI Wanna Dance With Somebody (Who Loves M=
e)=E2=80=9D because of a relationship with Larry Mestel, a Goldman client w=
ho has a relationship with the Houston estate. And:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Mr. Solomon became the bank=E2=80=99s chief ex=
ecutive in 2018, the same year Mr. Mestel=E2=80=99s Primary Wave became a G=
oldman client =E2=80=94 although another Goldman banker already had a relat=
ionship with the company. The following year, Mr. Mestel was named one of t=
he year=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9C100 Most Intriguing Entrepreneurs,=E2=80=9D an a=
nnual list published by Goldman. The list was a pet project of Mr. Solomon=
=E2=80=99s, according to a person with knowledge of the process.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CThere=E2=80=99s a kind of prima facie=
 appearance of: =E2=80=98you scratch my back, I scratch yours,=E2=80=99=E2=
=80=9D said Yaron Nili, an associate professor at the University of Wiscons=
in Law School who specializes in corporate and securities law.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Mr. Fratto said Mr. Solomon did not personally=
 pick Mr. Mestel for the list, and that there is =E2=80=9Cno economic compo=
nent=E2=80=9D to their relationship.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I want a congressional investigation of whethe=
r Mestel got on the =E2=80=9CMost Intriguing Entrepreneurs=E2=80=9D list as=
 a quid pro quo for getting Solomon the Whitney Houston remix rights. Discl=
osure, I used to work at Goldman, I like Goldman, I am basically rooting fo=
r its success, but if what=C2=A0brings down Goldman Sachs is a Whitney Hous=
ton remix quid pro quo scandal involving its DJ CEO I will laugh for a week=
 straight.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In other news from the 2018 Goldman succession=
 battle,=C2=A0here is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/cl=
ick/30484592.259448/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAyMy8wMi8wNi9idXNpbmV=
